            "title": "中國電力去年盈利增26%",
            "description": "<p>中國電力(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02380' >02380</a>)公布，截至去年底止，全年盈利33.64億元(人民幣．下同)，按年上升26.47%，每股盈利0.27元；派末期息0.162元。</p>\n<p>期內，收入542.13億元，按年增長22.48%。</p>   </div>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"hkej_hkex_notice_dl_btn_2014\">\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2025/0320/2025032001583_c.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">下載港交所通告原文</a>\n</div>\n        ",
